t: "O humanity! A lesson is set forth, so listen to it 斯carefully撕: those 斯idols撕 you invoke besides Allah can never create 斯so much as撕 a fly, even if they 斯all撕 were to come together for that. And if a fly were to snatch anything away from them, they cannot 斯even撕 retrieve it from the fly. How powerless are those who invoke and those invoked"